org.treetank.page

Class PageFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.treetank.page.PageFactory

  • public final class PageFactory
extends Object
    Factory to deserialize pages out of a chunk of bytes. This factory needs a INodeFactory-reference to perform inlying node-serializations as well.
    Author:
    Sebastian Graf, University of Konstanz
